The constructive production that survives F7/F8. At each good place the decoded surface's value roots the full GS interpolant (`Q(z, v(z)) = 0` — the GS list-membership cargo the `dvd_specialization_of_close` lane already produces); the interpolant factors `Q = ∏ᵢ Hᵢ`; over a field some factor vanishes per place; **pigeonhole over the m factors** hands one factor an incidence set of size `≥ |goodSet|/m`:

