- **C2 (the interpolant)**: `interpolatedRep s a₀ a₁ := linearShape (interpolant s a₀) (interpolant s a₁)` (:254) via `Lagrange.interpolate`, with `degreeX_interpolatedRep_le_one` (**`hdegX` by construction**), `natDegree_interpolatedRep_lt`, node-evaluation and tail-coefficient lemmas;
